<item>
            <title>[SOLR-16022] Improve security ui</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16022</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When changing user passwords through the Security UI, the password is required to follow a complexity pattern. It would be nice if this option were configurable as password length provides more entropy than the required password complexity. Either an enable/disable option or configurable settings would be nice.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Solr version: 8.11.1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;OS: CentOS Linux 7&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
